#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.power.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.power"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.power.power:1 of
msgid "First tensor elements raised to powers from second tensor, element-wise."
msgstr "第一个张量的元素按元素方式提升到第二个张量的幂次。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.power.power:3 of
msgid ""
"Raise each base in `x1` to the positionally-corresponding power in `x2`."
"  `x1` and `x2` must be broadcastable to the same shape. Note that an "
"integer type raised to a negative integer power will raise a ValueError."
msgstr ""
"将 `x1` 中的每个底数提升到 `x2` 中对应位置的幂次。`x1` 和 `x2` 必须可以"
"广播为相同形状。注意，整数类型提升到负整数幂次将会引发 ValueError。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.power.power of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.power.power:7 of
msgid "The bases."
msgstr "底数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.power.power:9 of
msgid "The exponents."
msgstr "指数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.power.power:11 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供了该参数，其形状必须与输入可广播一致。如果未"
"提供或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度"
"必须等于输出数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.power.power:16 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.power.power of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.power.power:21 of
msgid "**y** -- The bases in `x1` raised to the exponents in `x2`."
msgstr "**y** -- `x1` 中的底数提升到 `x2` 中的指数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.power.power of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.power.power:26 of
msgid ":py:obj:`float_power`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.power.power:27 of
msgid "power function that promotes integers to float"
msgstr "将整数提升为浮点数的幂函数"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.power.power:30 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.power.power:31 of
msgid "Cube each element in a list."
msgstr "对列表中的每个元素求立方。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.power.power:41 of
msgid "Raise the bases to different exponents."
msgstr "将底数提升到不同的指数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.power.power:47 of
msgid "The effect of broadcasting."
msgstr "广播的效果。"

